Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.45,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}令人興奮難抑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:30.08,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}七色音符  永劫綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:31.33,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}心中忐忑不安
