Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:37.38,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}玩夠了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:41.22,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}循於愛之真理  極光閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:42.85,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}差不多行了…
